<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-5">Faith services</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Prayer area<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">On-site chapel<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContent8f5e7d84397148bd93eff3d4801004d7">
</div>
<p>Â </p>
<p>We understand that coming to hospital can be a difficult and emotional time for lots of people.</p>
<p>If you are facing a time of illness, uncertainty or change you can meet with a member of our friendly <a href="https://www.imperial.nhs.uk/patients-and-visitors/chaplaincy-and-faith-services">chaplaincy team</a> who can provide emotional, pastoral and spiritual support, as well as a listening ear when you need it most.</p>
